This immaculate Tivoli floor plan is 2,398 sf, 3 bedrooms,2 bathrooms, including a separate office and a 3-car garage and screened porch. The community is guard gated 24 hours a day. Enjoy all the amenities that BELLALAGO offers including fitness center, entertainment and game rooms, saunas, Olympic sized heated pool and spa, water playground with slide, splash area, tennis and basketball courts, walking and bike trails to explore. Buyer to confirm all data and measurements pertaining to the property. We need at least 2 business days for a seller's response on all offers not including weekends.
